'''新尼亞姆茨修道院'''（{{lang-ro|Mănăstirea Noul Neamț}}）是位於[[聶斯特河沿岸|聶斯特河沿岸]]的一座男子[[摩爾多瓦正教會|摩爾多瓦正教會]][[修道院|修道院]]。修道院成立於1861年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.referat.ro/referate/Rena__351_terea_M_tirii_Noul_Neamt_06bab.htm |title=Renașterea mînăstirii Noul Neamț |access-date=2015-12-17 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927191756/http://www.referat.ro/referate/Rena__351_terea_M_tirii_Noul_Neamt_06bab.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1962年蘇聯政府關閉了修道院。1989年修道院重新開放。<ref>[http://www.crestinortodox.ro/Manastirea_Noul_Neamt___lavra_Basarabiei-24-289.html Noul Neamț monastery, article in "Lumea Credinței"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crestinortodox.ro/Manastirea_Noul_Neamt___lavra_Basarabiei-24-289.html |date=20081227011022 }} {{ro icon}}</ref>

